# Stack

- NextJS project with JavaScript
- Shadcn UI components
- Tailwind CSS
- Recharts
- Binance API to get crypto currencies balances
- Lucide react icons

# Description of the app

This app is a simulation of how much money a user colud have made if he would invested a certain amount of money in a certain time.The user should select a crypto coming from the coingecko API, fill the amount and date field and once he clics on Calcular button, he would have a recharts chart with the information of his simulated investment.